description:
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity to work at Liverpool Heart and Chest Hospital NHS Foundation Trust. We are a specialist Cardiac, Cardiology and Cardiothoracic Trust which has received consistent “outstanding” ratings by the CQC.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit caring, compassionate and highly motivated Registered Nurses to our cardio thoracic surgical teams. Whether you are an existing experienced Registered Nurse or a newly qualified Registered Nurse with an appetite for our specialism and an interest in joining our Trust we would love to hear from you. We offer locally agreed flexible working patterns and varying shift times, including long days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Registered Nurses for an interest within the surgical speciality The specialities include Cardiac surgery, Thoracic surgery and Upper Gastrointestinal surgery. We offer a full preceptorship package and continuous career development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an opportunity for candidates to join our team and develop their career across some very specialist areas in one of the few heart and chest focused hospitals in the country. We are looking for candidates who share our passion for patient and family centered care, have a strong belief in influencing the quality agenda, whilst supporting the development of nursing and medical colleagues alike. If you want to make a difference and be part of an outstanding team we look forward to your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to make a difference and be part of an outstanding team, please apply&lt;/p&gt;
